'''不想回家'''是一部中国内地电视连续剧，又名'''越陷越深'''。本剧于2005年10月在[[南京市|南京市]]拍摄<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新浪网 | title = 《不想回家》拍摄正酣，侯天来路过家门不回 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/x/2005-10-15/0625866098.html | author = 暴雪 | date = 2005-10-15 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | archive-date = 2019-09-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190914130343/http://ent.sina.com.cn/x/2005-10-15/0625866098.html }}</ref>
，2008年年在[[安徽卫视|安徽卫视]]、湖北卫视、[[江苏卫视|江苏卫视]]等各大电视台热播<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 荆楚网 | title = 热播情感剧引来观众热议 题材屡见不鲜让人厌倦 | url = http://news.cnhubei.com/ctdsb/ctdsbsgk/ctdsb36/200812/t513821.shtml | date = 2008-12-03 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | archive-date = 2019-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190912165734/http://news.cnhubei.com/ctdsb/ctdsbsgk/ctdsb36/200812/t513821.shtml }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新浪网 | title = 《不想回家》热播 侯天来：演不好对不起葛优 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-12-03/16512278107.shtml | author = 骆俊澎 | date = 2008年12月3日 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | archive-date = 2019-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190911232515/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-12-03/16512278107.shtml }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 新浪网 | title = 韩雪演富家女“不想回家” 两代人对话爱与生活 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-12-03/09532277281.shtml | date = 2008年12月3日 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | archive-date = 2019-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190912061458/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2008-12-03/09532277281.shtml }}</ref>
